    "description": "这是一款结合了国际象棋与时间回溯、时间棋子等机制的解谜游戏<br>通过这些机制可以带来很多有趣、复杂且充满深度的策略<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>通过消耗能量，可以将棋局回溯到过去的任意一个回合</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196000/extras/49ef6dbc79a624abdd0c8091261a4e8e.poster.avif?t=1727791236\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196000/extras/49ef6dbc79a624abdd0c8091261a4e8e.webm?t=1727791236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196000/extras/49ef6dbc79a624abdd0c8091261a4e8e.mp4?t=1727791236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>因回溯而暂时复活的棋子依然会在死亡的那个回合死掉，无法避免</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>时间棋子，一种不会受到时间回溯影响的棋子，无论是移动还是生死</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196000/extras/e2222c8f18712df7105b66626937f8ce.poster.avif?t=1727791236\" width=598 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196000/extras/e2222c8f18712df7105b66626937f8ce.webm?t=1727791236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196000/extras/e2222c8f18712df7105b66626937f8ce.mp4?t=1727791236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>因时间棋子的移动，可能会在导致过去的某一刻发生现实重叠现象……</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精妙的关卡</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>游戏有几大关卡，会层层递进展现给你时间象棋中的各种机制玩法</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>精心设计的关卡，思考整个时间线中的种种可呢能，给你极致的烧脑体验</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196000/extras/00cea113e19772ddd97b0bf080d0256a.poster.avif?t=1727791236\" width=600 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196000/extras/00cea113e19772ddd97b0bf080d0256a.webm?t=1727791236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196000/extras/00cea113e19772ddd97b0bf080d0256a.mp4?t=1727791236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>地图上还散落着隐藏的对战关卡哦……~</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >对战！</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>除了关卡模式以外，还有对战模式，可以用各种预设配置和电脑或本地对战 </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>通过在关卡模式中收集隐藏的对战关卡，来解锁更多的预设配置 </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>可以设定多样的参数，任何一个预设配置中都可以自由设定时间棋子</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196000/extras/5a567aa0c00484c63c144dc4f83dc419.poster.avif?t=1727791236\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196000/extras/5a567aa0c00484c63c144dc4f83dc419.webm?t=1727791236\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196000/extras/5a567aa0c00484c63c144dc4f83dc419.mp4?t=1727791236\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>（还可以让电脑对战电脑~！）</li></ul>",
